{
  "stem": "3097.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he worked first for a clinic, and now he works for the board of health, for the county board of health.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He probably will retire shortly, because he heard that I'm retiring, so he said he will retire too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The fourth one is Wasser-- W-A-S-S-E-R-- who was with me in the camp and escaped with me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He did immigrate here to United States, to Scranton, because he had family there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He, with his brother, opened a store there with some carpets, wall covering, and window dressing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And about eight years ago, he did expire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He was sick.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He had cancer of the colon and he did die.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "His wife is alive, in Scranton, Pennsylvania, and I am in quite close touch with her [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, first of all the kids, you see, they tried to beat us up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No question about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Always, there was some-- some problems, you see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I could-- even, let's say, if I would have gone-- if I would like to go to a public, or-- or-- or it was a state high school, I couldn't get in.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe [INAUDIBLE] I would be a genius, maybe they would make an exception or something like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I was not a genius, and I didn't even try, because there would be no-- no chance.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all those things what I say, it was very, very difficult and you go-- you went to the park-- there was a park, a lagoon, in our city-- and you go spend some time, you were afraid because of the incidents, hooligan incidents.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- I was a kid, actually.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My life was more concentrated in the school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't know too many people outside the school.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
